source.name: Oregon Workers' Compensation Employers and Accepted Disabling Claims
source.description: In 1968, most Oregon employers became subject to Oregon’s workers’ compensation statute. The table provides some information for much of the life of the workers’ compensation system. Descriptions of the data series are provided in an attached document.
